00:08:08.720 --> 00:08:12.720
Well, thankfully, technology has evolved.

00:08:13.520 --> 00:08:16.136
And there are now machines

00:08:16.160 --> 00:08:19.776
that can process fonio
in a more efficient way.

00:08:19.800 --> 00:08:22.176
And as a matter of fact,

00:08:22.200 --> 00:08:23.816
a few years ago,

